name: Nancye Green
biography:
Nancye Green - Founding partner with Michael Donovan, Donovan and Green, now part of CKS.
Bachelor's degree in Political Science, Newcomb College, Tulane University.
Additional studies at Parsons School of Design.
Member, Board of Directors, Hallmark Cards.
Past President, American Institute of Graphic Arts and Internatioal Design Conference, Aspen, Colorado.
1998  Honorary degree, Fine Arts, Corcoran School of Art.
Executive Partner, USWeb/CKS.

Source: www.understabdubgusa/com, December 2001.
